&ccedil;i&#351;megini&#328; alamatlary bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Bir sinusy&#328;
izol&yacute;asi&yacute;a &ccedil;i&#351;megi gaty se&yacute;rekdir (5%
&yacute;agda&yacute;ynda), k&ouml;plen&ccedil; lukmanlar bir wagty&#328;
&ouml;z&uuml;nde birn&auml;&ccedil;e sinusy&#328; &yacute;e&#328;ilmegi bilen
&yacute;&uuml;zbe-&yacute;&uuml;z bol&yacute;arlar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Alamatlar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Katarral alamatlar - Bu burun bo&#351;lugyny, dykylmagy,
&uuml;sg&uuml;lewigi we sowuklama bilen baglany&#351;ykly be&yacute;leki
alamatlary &ouml;z i&ccedil;ine al&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Sinusiti&#328; wirusly
tebigaty bilen akymy&#328; mukdary, a&ccedil;-a&ccedil;anlygy we
&yacute;akymsyz ysy &yacute;ok.&nbsp;Bakteri&yacute;a &ouml;s&uuml;mlik
d&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;si birikdirilende, &yacute;akymsyz ys bilen k&ouml;p
mukdarda arassalanma bol&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Kellagyry sinusiti&#328; esasy alamatlaryndan
biridir.&nbsp;K&ouml;plen&ccedil; &yacute;agda&yacute;da agyry &yacute;okarky
lokalizasi&yacute;a bolmazdan, &yacute;okarky e&#328;ege, di&#351;lere,
ybadathana &yacute;a&yacute;ramak bilen gow&#351;ak &yacute;a-da orta
intensiwlikde &yacute;a&yacute;ra&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&#350;e&yacute;le-de bolsa,
bir sinusy&#328; g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;li &ccedil;i&#351;megi bilen agyry
sindromyny&#328; belli bir tebigatyny g&ouml;rmek bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&#350;e&yacute;lelik
bilen, frontal sinuslary&#328; &ccedil;i&#351;megi bilen agyry
ma&#328;la&yacute;da lokalla&#351;&yacute;ar, g&ouml;&ccedil;me kelle agyrysyna
me&#328;ze&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Sfenoid sinus t&auml;sir edilende, oksipital
sebitde agyry &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;yk&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Agyry esasan
infraorbital sebitde bolsa, burun k&ouml;pr&uuml;sini&#328; sebitinde sinusiti&#328;
d&ouml;remegi - etmoidit (etmoid sinusy&#328; &ccedil;i&#351;megi) hakda
pikirlenmeli.&nbsp;K&auml;bir hadysalarda sin&uuml;ziti&#328; agyryly
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;leri &yacute;&uuml;z&uuml;&#328; s&uuml;&#328;k
gurlu&#351;laryna degeninde we degeninde &yacute;akymsyz du&yacute;gular bilen
&ccedil;&auml;klen&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Be&yacute;leki h&auml;si&yacute;etli alamatlar
serho&#351;lygy&#328; (gyzzyrma, gow&#351;aklyk, my&#351;sa agyrylary),
sebitd&auml;ki limfa d&uuml;w&uuml;nlerini&#328; ulalmagy, burnu&#328;
gyjyndyrylmagy (k&ouml;melek &yacute;okan&ccedil;lygy bilen), ys
du&yacute;gusyny&#328; peselmegi, i&#351;d&auml;&#328; peselmegi we be&yacute;leki
belli bolmadyk alamatlary &ouml;z i&ccedil;ine al&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Alamatlary&#328; agyrlygy
&yacute;okan&ccedil; prosesi&#328; d&ouml;remegine seb&auml;p
bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Wirus we k&ouml;melek sin&uuml;ziti has a&#328;sat,
bakterial sinusit has agyrdyr we bejergini&#328; gijikdirilmegi k&ouml;p
kyn&ccedil;ylyklara we &yacute;ygy-&yacute;ygydan ga&yacute;talanmalara
seb&auml;p bolup biler.&nbsp;10 &yacute;a&#351;a &ccedil;enli &ccedil;agalar
&uuml;sg&uuml;lew&uuml;k, bokurdak agyry, burun akmagy we gyzzyrma &yacute;aly
umumy alamatlary&#328; agdyklyk etmegi bilen
h&auml;si&yacute;etlendiril&yacute;&auml;r, &#351;onu&#328; &uuml;&ccedil;in
&ccedil;agany&#328; &yacute;agda&yacute;yna &uuml;nsli bolmak we keseli&#328;
ilkinji alamatlarynda lukmana &yacute;&uuml;z tutmak m&ouml;h&uuml;mdir.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Keseli&#328; diagnozy</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Sorag we g&ouml;zleg</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Otorinolaringolog bilen
du&#351;u&#351;mak, n&auml;sag bilen s&ouml;hbetde&#351;lik ge&ccedil;irmekden,
keseli&#328; esasy &#351;ika&yacute;atlaryny we anamnezini anyklamakdan,
t&ouml;wekgel&ccedil;ilik faktorlaryny&#328; bardygyny kesgitlemekden
ba&#351;la&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Lukman hassany&#328; umumy &yacute;agda&yacute;yna
baha ber&yacute;&auml;r; sinuslary&#328; pro&yacute;eksi&yacute;asynda zarba
urmak (kakmak) zerurdyr.&nbsp;Barlagda, rinoskopi&yacute;a
ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r - burun bo&#351;lugyny burun dilatorlaryny we
a&yacute;nalaryny ulanyp barlamak.&nbsp;Wizual baha bermek bilen,
giperemi&yacute;a (gyzarma) we wazokonstriktor dermanlaryny&#328;
orna&#351;magyna jogap h&ouml;km&uuml;nde gow&#351;ak reaksi&yacute;a
d&ouml;red&yacute;&auml;n, k&auml;mahal sianotik mukoza
kesgitlen&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Rinoskopi&yacute;a, patogeni&#328; deslapky
kesgitlenmegi we bejergini&#328; taktikasyny kesgitlemek &uuml;&ccedil;in
m&ouml;h&uuml;m bolan b&ouml;l&uuml;nip &ccedil;yk&yacute;an sekresi&yacute;any
jikme-jik &ouml;wrenm&auml;ge m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik ber&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Laboratori&yacute;a barlagy</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Kliniki gan barlagy - adaty kliniki gan synagynda
&ccedil;i&#351;me keselleri bilen, le&yacute;kositozy&#328; le&yacute;kosit
formulasyny&#328; &ccedil;epe ge&ccedil;megi (ne&yacute;trofilleri&#328;
sanyny&#328; k&ouml;pelmegi), ESR-i&#328; &yacute;okarlanmagy bilen
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;yk&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Uteiti sin&uuml;zitde &uuml;&yacute;tge&#351;meler
has a&yacute;dy&#328; g&ouml;r&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Dowamly
&yacute;uwa&#351;lyk prosesinde der&#328;ewd&auml;ki
&uuml;&yacute;tge&#351;meler az bol&yacute;ar &yacute;a-da asla kesgitlenme&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>C-reaktiw belok, biohimiki gan indeksidir, bu k&ouml;pelmek
bedeni&#328; &yacute;iti &ccedil;i&#351;me reaksi&yacute;asyny
g&ouml;rkez&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;C-reaktiw belogy&#328; &yacute;okary derejesi
sin&uuml;ziti&#328; bakterial h&auml;si&yacute;etini
g&ouml;rkez&yacute;&auml;r, wirus &yacute;a-da k&ouml;melek
&yacute;okan&ccedil;lygy bilen has aram &yacute;okarlan&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Zy&#328;yly&#351;y&#328; bakteriologiki g&ouml;zden
ge&ccedil;irmesi - t&auml;sirli antibiotik bejergisini sa&yacute;lamak
&uuml;&ccedil;in zerur bolan belli bir patogenini kesgitlemek &uuml;&ccedil;in
sinuslardan ak&yacute;an suw sepmek.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Sitologiki g&ouml;zden ge&ccedil;irmek (rinositogramma) -
mikroskopik enjamlary ulanyp, burun bo&#351;lugyndan &ccedil;ykmagy
barlamak.&nbsp;Sin&uuml;zit bilen &ccedil;i&#351;megi&#328; umumy alamatlary
kesgitlen&yacute;&auml;r: le&yacute;kositleri&#328; we lenfositleri&#328;,
mukusy&#328;, desumirlenen epiteli&#328; sanyny&#328; k&ouml;pelmegi.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Funksional, radiasi&yacute;a
we instrumental diagnostika</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Burun bo&#351;lugyny we sinuslary endoskopiki g&ouml;zden
ge&ccedil;irmek, burun bo&#351;lugyny&#328;, nasofarinksi&#328; we paranazal
sinuslary&#328; nemli membranasyny wizual g&ouml;zden ge&ccedil;irmek
&uuml;&ccedil;in in&ccedil;e endoskop arkaly ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Ial&uuml;z rentgen, paranazal sinuslary emele getir&yacute;&auml;n
s&uuml;&#328;kleri&#328; rentgen barlagydyr.&nbsp;Radiografi&yacute;any&#328;
k&ouml;megi bilen &ccedil;i&#351;m&auml;ni&#328;, suwuklygy&#328;
(eksudaty&#328;) bardygyny kesgitlemek bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;G&ouml;zleg, has
gowusy frontal we gapdal pro&yacute;eksi&yacute;alarda oturgy&ccedil;da
ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Burun bo&#351;lugyny&#328; KT (hasaplanan tomografi&yacute;asy),
gatlak-gatlak &#351;ekilleri&#328; (dilimleri&#328;) emele gelmegi bilen
rentgen barlagyna esaslan&yacute;an usuldyr.&nbsp;Synag, &yacute;&ouml;rite
anatomiki gurlu&#351;y jikme-jik &ouml;wrenm&auml;ge m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik
ber&yacute;&auml;r, s&uuml;&#328;k skeletini&#328; anomali&yacute;alaryny,
&ccedil;i&#351;me alamatlaryny&#328; we k&ouml;p&ccedil;&uuml;ligi&#328;
bardygyny &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykar&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Uteiti sin&uuml;zit
&yacute;a-da onu&#328; kyn&ccedil;ylyklary &uuml;&ccedil;in operasi&yacute;a
me&yacute;ille&#351;dirilende KT amala a&#351;yryl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Paranazal sinuslary&#328; de&#351;ilmegi - mazmuny&#328;
ymtyly&#351;y we so&#328;raky bakteriologiki g&ouml;zleg bilen sinusy&#328;
de&#351;ilmegi.&nbsp;Bu amal bejeri&#351; maksady bilen hem amala a&#351;yrylyp
bilner, bu &yacute;agda&yacute;da &yacute;erli bejergi &uuml;&ccedil;in
de&#351;ilen i&#328;&#328;&auml;ni&#328; &uuml;sti bilen bejeri&#351;
&ccedil;&ouml;zg&uuml;di sanjym edil&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Rhinomanometri&yacute;a, &yacute;&ouml;rite rinomanometr enjamyny
ulanyp, burun dem al&#351;yny&#328; i&#351;ini &ouml;wrenmekdir.&nbsp;Bu usul,
burun bo&#351;lugyny&#328; we paranazal sinuslary&#328; &ccedil;i&#351;
kesellerinde &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;yk&yacute;an howa akymyny&#328;
tizligini&#328; peselmegini &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykar&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi maksatlary</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Uteiti sin&uuml;ziti
bejermegi&#328; maksady &yacute;okan&ccedil; prosesi&#328; d&ouml;remegine
seb&auml;p bol&yacute;an seri&#351;d&auml;ni &yacute;ok etmek, burun dem
aly&#351; i&#351;ini dikeltmek we dowamlylygy&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni
almakdyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Dowamly sin&uuml;zitde
di&#328;e bir ulalma &yacute;ygylygyny azaltmak bilen
&ccedil;&auml;klenm&auml;n, me&yacute;ille&#351;dirilen hirurgiki
&ccedil;&auml;releri&#328; k&ouml;megi bilen keseli&#328; esasy seb&auml;bini
(anatomiki binag&auml;rlik bozulan &yacute;agda&yacute;ynda) &yacute;ok etmek
&uuml;&ccedil;in hem tagalla etmek m&ouml;h&uuml;mdir.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Sin&uuml;ziti&#328; bejergisi
&ccedil;yl&#351;yrymly we a&yacute;ratyn bolmaly, konserwatiw we hirurgiki
bejergini&#328; usullaryny &ouml;z i&ccedil;ine almalydyr (zerur bolsa).</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351; &yacute;oly we
gurallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Sinusitden
&#351;&uuml;bhelen&yacute;&auml;n bolsa, n&auml;sag sowuk howa, senagat tozany
bilen aragatna&#351;ykdan ga&ccedil;a durmalydyr we di&#351; lukmanyna
gitmekden saklanmalydyr.&nbsp;Bu amal gi&#328;den &yacute;a&yacute;ran bolsa
(pansinusit), umumy serho&#351;lyk alamatlary azal&yacute;an&ccedil;a 5-7
g&uuml;n&uuml;&#328; dowamynda d&uuml;&#351;ekde dyn&ccedil; almak
bellenil&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Keselhanada hassahana &yacute;erle&#351;dirilmegi
ambulatori&yacute;a esasynda bejergini&#328; netijesizligi, yiringli kyn&ccedil;ylyklary&#328;
d&ouml;remegi we agyr birle&#351;&yacute;&auml;n patologi&yacute;alarda
g&ouml;rkezil&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Dermanlar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Derman bejergisi patogeni&#328;
&yacute;ok edilmegine, &ccedil;i&#351;me prosesini azaltmaga, &#351;e&yacute;le
hem burun dem al&#351;yny&#328; bozulan funksi&yacute;alaryny &yacute;ok
etm&auml;ge g&ouml;n&uuml;kdirilendir.&nbsp;Ne&#351;e seri&#351;delerini&#328;
a&#351;akdaky toparlary ulanyl&yacute;ar:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Antibakterial dermanlar - k&ouml;plen&ccedil; &yacute;okan&ccedil;
seri&#351;d&auml;ni &yacute;ok etm&auml;ge g&ouml;n&uuml;kdirilen k&ouml;p
sanly derman seri&#351;deleri ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Ildum&#351;ak we orta
agyrlykdaky sin&uuml;zit &uuml;&ccedil;in plan&#351;et g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;i
ulanyl&yacute;ar, agyr g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;i bilen, derman seri&#351;desini
&ouml;&yacute;j&uuml;kli sanjym g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;inde &yacute;a-da damja
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;inde bell&auml;p bol&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Antihistaminikler antibakterial seri&#351;deler bilen bilelikde
gyjyndyrmany&#328; &ccedil;i&#351;mesini &yacute;ok etmek, &#351;e&yacute;le
hem antibiotiklere allergiki t&auml;sirleri&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak
&uuml;&ccedil;in ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Steroid d&auml;l &ccedil;i&#351;m&auml; gar&#351;y dermanlar,
&ccedil;i&#351;m&auml; gar&#351;y, antipiretiki we analjezik t&auml;sirleri
bolan dermanlardyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Wazokonstriktor seri&#351;deleri (dekongestantlar) burun demini
gowula&#351;dyryp, dekonjestant we vazokonstriktor t&auml;sirine
e&yacute;e.&nbsp;Sowuklyga gar&#351;y &ccedil;yl&#351;yrymly dermanlary&#328;
bir b&ouml;legi h&ouml;km&uuml;nde we spre&yacute;ler we burun damjalary
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;inde &yacute;erli ulanmak &uuml;&ccedil;in
&ouml;nd&uuml;ril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Mukolitikler sekresi&yacute;any&#328; &yacute;apy&#351;ygyny
peseld&yacute;&auml;r we akymyny gowulandyr&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Paranazal
sinuslardan &ccedil;i&#351;me eksudatyny&#328; &ccedil;ykmagyna k&ouml;mek
edi&#328;, &ccedil;i&#351;megi azald&yacute;ar we burun demini
kadala&#351;dyr&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Gl&yacute;ukokortikoid dermanlary, &ccedil;i&#351;m&auml;
gar&#351;y, dekonjestant we ara&ccedil;ylyk bakterisid t&auml;siri bilen
&yacute;erli gormonal dermanlardyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>A&yacute;dylan
&ccedil;i&#351;me we kyn&ccedil;ylyklary&#328; &ouml;smegi bilen, gurallary
bejermek proseduralary g&ouml;rkezil&yacute;&auml;r:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Sinus kateterini ulanyp sekresi&yacute;alara ymtylmak, burun
bo&#351;lugynda we paranazal sinuslarda basy&#351; tapawudyny
d&ouml;retm&auml;ge esaslan&yacute;an invaziv proseduradyr.&nbsp;Turbalary&#328;
we silindrleri&#328; &yacute;&ouml;rite ulgamyny ulanmak arkaly amala
a&#351;yryl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Bu usul sinuslary&#328; mazmunyny
si&#328;dirm&auml;ge, &#351;e&yacute;le hem &yacute;erli bejerg&auml;
dermanlary sanjym etm&auml;ge m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik ber&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Terapewtiki punksi&yacute;a - deslapky anestezi bilen paranazal sinusy&#328;
de&#351;igi.&nbsp;Ex&ouml;rite de&#351;ilen i&#328;&#328;&auml;ni&#328;
k&ouml;megi bilen &yacute;erine &yacute;etiril&yacute;&auml;r, onu&#328;
&uuml;sti bilen eksudat islen&yacute;&auml;r we dermanlyk erginler
gu&yacute;ul&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Ponksion, yiringli &ccedil;i&#351;m&auml;ni&#328;
kesgitlenen hakykaty bilen stasionar &#351;ertlerde amala
a&#351;yryl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Sinusit bejergisinde k&ouml;p
sanly fizioterapewtiki amallar hem ulanyl&yacute;ar (magnitoterapi&yacute;a,
derman elektroforezi, UHF bejergisi we &#351;.m.).</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki bejergisi,
&yacute;eterlik howa howa hereketine p&auml;sgel ber&yacute;&auml;n
s&uuml;&#328;k gurlu&#351;laryny&#328; dogabitdi &yacute;a-da gazanylan (trawma
netijesinde) deformasi&yacute;asyny &yacute;ok etmek, &#351;e&yacute;le hem
yiringli kyn&ccedil;ylyklary &yacute;ok etmek &uuml;&ccedil;in
ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Sinusy&#328; a&ccedil;ylmagyny we
arassalanan zatlary a&yacute;yrmagy maksat edin&yacute;&auml;r, so&#328; bolsa
s&uuml;&#328;kleri gys&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Amallar minimal invaziv &yacute;a-da
endonazal, adaty &yacute;a-da ekstranasal
b&ouml;l&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Hirurgiki gaty&#351;ma usuly hassany&#328;
umumy &yacute;agda&yacute;yny, &ccedil;yl&#351;yrymlylygy&#328;
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;ini we hassahanany&#328; tehniki kuwwatyny g&ouml;z
&ouml;&#328;&uuml;nde tutup kesgitlen&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;y&#328; hilini
dikeltmek we gowula&#351;dyrmak</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Uteiti sin&uuml;ziti&#328;
amatly ugry bar we &yacute;&ouml;rite reabilitasi&yacute;a &ccedil;&auml;releri
talap edilme&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;N&auml;sagda uzak wagtlap dowam
ed&yacute;&auml;n sinusit bar bolsa, dowamly prosesi&#328;
g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;lenmegine seb&auml;p bol&yacute;an &ouml;j&uuml;kdiriji
faktorlary (sowuklama, allergenler bilen aragatna&#351;yk, dowamly
keselleri&#328; dekompensasi&yacute;asy, senagat tozany bilen baglany&#351;yk
we &#351;.m.) &yacute;ok etmek maslahat beril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>M&uuml;mkin kyn&ccedil;ylyklar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Sin&uuml;zit bilen
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;yk&yacute;an kyn&ccedil;ylyklar, esasan, keseli&#328;
5-7-nji g&uuml;n&uuml;nde, yiringli &ccedil;i&#351;me prosesini&#328;
t&ouml;weregind&auml;ki dokumalara &yacute;a&yacute;ramagy bilen
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;yk&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Bu derrew hassahana
&yacute;erle&#351;dirilmegi we k&auml;bir &yacute;agda&yacute;larda operasi&yacute;a
&uuml;&ccedil;in g&ouml;ni g&ouml;rkezme.&nbsp;Bu kyn&ccedil;ylyklar
&#351;ulary &ouml;z i&ccedil;ine al&yacute;ar:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Kavernoz sinus trombozy, sinusy&#328; tromb bilen bir-birine gabat
gelmegi seb&auml;pli be&yacute;niden wena akymyny&#328;
bozulmagydyr.&nbsp;Tromboz, &ccedil;i&#351;me prosesi sinusdan wena sinusyna
&yacute;a&yacute;ranso&#328;, damar diwaryny&#328; &ccedil;i&#351;megi we gan
damarlaryny&#328; emele gelmegi bilen &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;yk&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Periostit - katarraly&#328; we yiringli
&ccedil;i&#351;m&auml;ni&#328; emele gelmegi bilen periosteumy&#328;
&ccedil;i&#351;megi.&nbsp;Periostiti&#328; d&ouml;remegini&#328; esasy alamaty,
sinuslary&#328; pro&yacute;eksi&yacute;a me&yacute;danyna basylanda &yacute;iti
agyrydyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Periosteal abses, yiringli periostiti&#328; netijesidir.&nbsp;Bu
&yacute;agda&yacute;da, arassalanan infiltrasi&yacute;a periosteumdan
encapsul&yacute;asi&yacute;a we iri&#328; bilen doldurylan
&ccedil;&auml;klendirilen bo&#351;lugy&#328; emele gelmegi bilen a&yacute;ryl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Orbital sell&yacute;ulit, orbital dokumalary&#328;
&yacute;a&yacute;ran yiringli &ccedil;i&#351;mesi bolup, agyr serho&#351;lyk,
agyry, g&ouml;r&uuml;&#351;i&#328; peselmegi bilen t&auml;sir
edil&yacute;&auml;n g&ouml;z&uuml;&#328; k&ouml;rl&uuml;gine &ccedil;enli
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;yk&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Ntrakranial kyn&ccedil;ylyklar, &ccedil;i&#351;i&#328; kranial
bo&#351;luga &yacute;a&yacute;ramagy bilen baglany&#351;ykly i&#328;
&ccedil;yl&#351;yrymly kyn&ccedil;ylyklardan biridir.&nbsp;&#350;e&yacute;le
kyn&ccedil;ylyklary&#328; d&ouml;remeginde, birle&#351;&yacute;&auml;n keselleri&#328;
fonunda immuniteti&#328; peselmegi, &#351;e&yacute;le hem ne&#351;e
seri&#351;delerini&#328; g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;iliksiz kabul edilmegi
m&ouml;h&uuml;m rol o&yacute;na&yacute;ar (mysal &uuml;&ccedil;in,
antibiotikleri &yacute;ygy-&yacute;ygydan ulanmak gar&#351;ylygy&#328;
&ouml;smegine we &yacute;oklugyna seb&auml;p bolup biler) bejergini&#328;
fonunda bejergini&#328; t&auml;siri).&nbsp;&#350;e&yacute;le
kyn&ccedil;ylyklary arahnoidit (be&yacute;nini&#328; arahnoid
membranasyny&#328; &ccedil;i&#351;megi), intrakranial absesler we meningit
bilen a&#328;ladyp biler.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351;
&ccedil;&auml;releri</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>I&#351;je&#328; durmu&#351; &yacute;&ouml;relgesi;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&ccedil;ilimi ta&#351;lamak;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&yacute;okarky dem aly&#351; &yacute;ollaryny&#328;
&yacute;okan&ccedil;lyklaryny wagtynda bejermek;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>agyz arassa&ccedil;ylygyny yzygiderli &yacute;erine
&yacute;etirmek we di&#351;leri&#328; &yacute;agda&yacute;yna
g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik etmek;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>birle&#351;&yacute;&auml;n somatiki keselleri&#328; gidi&#351;ini
g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilikde sakla&#328;;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>g&ouml;rkezilen bolsa - anatomiki anomali&yacute;alar
&uuml;&ccedil;in me&yacute;ille&#351;dirilen hirurgiki gaty&#351;magy amala
a&#351;yrmak;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>howply pudaklarda i&#351;l&auml;n wagty&#328;yz &#351;ahsy gorag
&ccedil;&auml;relerini ulany&#328;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ccedil;aklama</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Wagtynda bejermek bilen,
&ccedil;aklama amatly.&nbsp;Se&yacute;rek &yacute;agda&yacute;larda hroniki
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;e ge&ccedil;mek we bakteri&yacute;a
kyn&ccedil;ylyklaryny&#328; d&ouml;remegi m&uuml;mkindir.&nbsp;Bu
&yacute;agda&yacute;da &ccedil;aklama, &ccedil;yl&#351;yrymlylygy&#328;
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;ine we bejergini&#328; dogrulygyna baglydyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Lukmandan ha&yacute;sy
soraglary bermeli?</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Sinusiti&#328; d&ouml;remegine n&auml;me seb&auml;p bolup biler?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
